---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Journaling Techniques">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="bg-[#fafafa] pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-0 px-0 overflow-x-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      
      <section class="text-center mb-16 md:mb-24">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
          The most important conversation you will ever have is the <span class="text-indigo-600 block sm:inline">one you have with yourself.</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-base md:text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed">
            Journaling Techniques was built because most people know they should journal, but no one ever taught them how. Hundreds of methods and research are scattered where most people never find them—we built this place to change that.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
        <div class="mb-8 text-center md:text-left">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight">What We Write About</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2 font-medium">Writing about your life changes how you live it.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[32px] md:rounded-[40px] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
               <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9.663 17h4.674M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Journaling Techniques</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">
              Over 48 research-supported methods like Gratitude Journaling and Morning Pages, explained with real prompts.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[32px] md:rounded-[40px] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-rose-50 text-rose-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
               <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Daily Life Writing</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">
              Processing frustrations, capturing unexpected joys, and reflecting on the slow growth visible over months.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16 md:mb-24 py-10 md:py-12 border-y border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6 text-center md:text-left">Why This Exists</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 text-slate-600 text-base md:text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-center md:text-left">
            <p>There is a gap between knowing journaling is good for you and actually doing it in a way that feels meaningful.</p>
            <p class="text-slate-900 font-bold">We are here to say: you are doing it right if you are doing it at all.</p>
            <p>This site exists to lower the barrier, providing the techniques and encouragement to keep going.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-24 md:mb-32">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 md:gap-12 items-start">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 md:sticky md:top-32">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-[32px] md:rounded-[40px] border border-slate-100 text-center shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 md:w-24 md:h-24 bg-slate-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 md:mb-6"></div>
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">John Miller</h3>
              <p class="text-indigo-600 font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Founder & Specialist</p>
              <div class="mt-6 md:mt-8 space-y-3 text-left">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-black text-slate-500 uppercase"><span class="text-base">📓</span> 10+ Years Practice</div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-black text-slate-500 uppercase"><span class="text-base">🔬</span> Research Driven</div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-black text-slate-500 uppercase"><span class="text-base">✍️</span> 48+ Techniques</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight text-center md:text-left">The Story Behind the Pen</h2>
            <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base font-medium leading-relaxed space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
              <p>John Miller has spent over a decade writing every single day. He discovered that writing about your life is powerful for your mind and health.</p>
              <blockquote class="text-lg md:text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 border-l-4 md:border-l-8 border-indigo-600 pl-4 md:pl-8 py-2 md:py-4 my-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-r-2xl">
                "Journaling is not about becoming a better writer. It is about becoming a more honest thinker."
              </blockquote>
              <p>He built this site to be the resource he wished existed when he first picked up a pen.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <section id="contact" class="w-full bg-[#0f172a] text-white py-20 md:py-32 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight">Write for Us</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-base md:text-xl mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">
          We welcome contributions from writers and journalers who have something genuine to say. If you have lived it or practiced it, we want to read your pitch.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-16 text-left">
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-indigo-400 text-xl block mb-2">✓</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300">Original Only</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-indigo-400 text-xl block mb-2">✓</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300">Min 800 Words</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-indigo-400 text-xl block mb-2">✓</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300">No AI Content</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-indigo-400 text-xl block mb-2">✓</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300">Grounded Pieces</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">Ready to contribute?</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@journalingtechniques.org" class="inline-block bg-white text-slate-900 px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-black text-sm md:text-lg hover:bg-indigo-500 hover:text-white transition-all transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
            hello@journalingtechniques.org
          </a>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs font-medium pt-4 italic">We respond within 7 to 10 business days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>